          Ao migrar para o GetNexo, voc√™ n√£o est√° apenas trocando de software. Voc√™ est√° atualizando sua empresa para a era da <strong>IA Generativa</strong>.
          Enquanto o {comp.name} foca em conectar cabos, n√≥s focamos em fechar vendas.
        </p>

        <div class="not-prose mt-12 p-8 bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-900/40 to-[#00ff9d]/10 rounded-2xl border border-[#00ff9d]/20 text-center">
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Migra√ß√£o Gratuita</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-300 mb-8">
            Nossa equipe ajuda voc√™ a importar seus contatos e fluxos do {comp.name} para o GetNexo. Sem dor de cabe√ßa.
          </p>
          <a href="/criar-bot" class="btn-primary-glow">Iniciar Migra√ß√£o Agora</a>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</Layout>

<style>
  .battle-hero { padding: 4rem 0 2rem; }
  .hero-badge { background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05); color: #94a3b8; padding: 0.5rem 1.2rem; border-radius: 50px; font-weight: 700; display: inline-block; font-size: 0.8rem; letter-spacing: 1px; text-transform: uppercase; }
  
  .comp-item { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; padding-bottom: 0.5rem; border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.05); }
  .comp-item .label { color: #94a3b8; font-size: 0.9rem; font-weight: 600; text-transform: uppercase; }
  .comp-item .value { font-weight: 700; text-align: right; max-width: 60%; }
  
  .comp-item.positive .value { color: #00ff9d; }
  .comp-item.negative .value { color: #f87171; }
  .comp-item.neutral .value { color: #cbd5e1; }

  .btn-primary-glow { display: inline-block; background: linear-gradient(135deg, #00d4ff, #00ff9d); color: black; padding: 1rem 2.5rem; border-radius: 12px; font-weight: 800; text-decoration: none; transition: 0.3s; box-shadow: 0 5px 20px rgba(0, 255, 157, 0.3); }
  .btn-primary-glow:hover { transform: translateY(-2px); box-shadow: 0 10px 40px rgba(0, 255, 157, 0.5); }
</style>
